item.description:
Hey!! In celebration of the Stonebridge Bistro getting their FULL liquor license, there will be an All Out Acoustic Jam there on Saturday Night, March 12th, beginning at 9:00 pm!! Bring some friends and your thirst for a good time and good music!!! Bring your instruments of peace and join us!!!!

 

I'm going to get there at 830 in order to get a good seat. I hope to see you guys there!
item.how_to_find_us: just look for the loud bunch
